{"tid":1251941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"623 臺北白衣反送中+反紅色媒體大遊行","createTime":"2019-06-22T17:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T09:20:04.000Z","uid":258706,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9efd43aa5cd014c54011e997e08015fa82cbdd","tid":1251941,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"6月23日輪到臺北搞反紅色媒體+聲援反送中大遊行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source : <a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2821950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821950&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=6dbe11f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821950&h=1d119dec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2821950</a></span><br />\n公道講一句，其實真心想多謝好多臺灣人喺反送中風潮入面咁支持香港人，又搞集會，又搞遊行撐我地<br />\n佢地2014年搞太陽花學運反服貿、反經濟赤化果陣，香港好似都冇乜大反應 or 大型民間應援行動 <br />\n但睇返臺灣既新聞網，臺灣人呢幾個星期搞左至少10個反送中集會，D臺灣既大學仲夾份拍左條聯合聲援既片，甚至有臺北學生同我地一齊罷課<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source ：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%88%87%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=7d4fa996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%88%87%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a></span><br />\n對比起香港，引渡條例其實對臺灣冇咁大逼切性同影響，佢地其實可以隔岸觀火同唔一定要咁大反應同行動<br />\n但佢地都照企出黎、行出黎同我地一齊向剝削人權同毀滅香港既條例say no <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔知連登呢度多唔多識港式中文既臺灣人睇<br />\n如果你係居港臺人或者係香港既臺灣留學/畢業生，想用臺語同你講返一聲：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">k&aacute;m-siā ！k&aacute;m-siā ！</span></span>"},{"pid":"eff06f2636e4286f95922cd56c9d3cb6e80911d3","tid":1251941,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b60f031579d1bd9586f0cdb5b69777955e5140f9","tid":1251941,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e649096c5464bba71c9767697861c095f0e0e0fe","tid":1251941,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"唇亡齒寒"},{"pid":"61ef6e78f5d2c20c85d145de70bd54a911ec4b8e","tid":1251941,"uid":41477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"台灣仲多廢中廢老<br />\n真係信得把口既韓國瑜就死得"},{"pid":"535b16abc7b6fd9b38de52d896fe62109b2de9e7","tid":1251941,"uid":262263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159497f9d42a027256adaba80e517ba4256d9bc3","tid":1251941,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"933033df237790d6dfb2435e5eca74b0f3daf751","tid":1251941,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6887a9ab1f7ac3c120029146d29c3d76d767970e","tid":1251941,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"159497f9d42a027256adaba80e517ba4256d9bc3","tid":1251941,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime